ğŸš€ Quickstart

Initialize a new evaluation workspace:
```bash
trainloop init
```

Run an evaluation using your configured LLM judge:
```bash
trainloop eval
```

Launch the interactive â€œstudioâ€ UI in your browser:
```bash
trainloop studio
# then open http://localhost:8080
```

